actions.message:
`Setreportchannel`:sets a report channel.
`Report`:reports a user.
`Membercount`:gives you the membercount of your server.
`Botstatus`:gives you the bot status.
`SimpleSetUp`:a simple channels setup for your new discord servers. *doesn't mess with the premissions, it will be updated to tho.*
`Announcement`:makes an announcement.
`Suggest`:needs a channel named suggestions inorded to work.
`Urban`:uses the urban site for translation.
`qoute`:gives you a random qoute.
`Fact`:gives you a random fact.

actions.message:
`Kiss, Pat, Feed, Cuddle, Poke, Tickle, Slap, Hug,`:basic anime interactions
`Fight`: tag a user to fight them.
`Punch`: only works if you're already in a fight with someone.
`Bite`: only works if you're already in a fight with someone.
`Gold`: shows you the amount of gold you have.
`Ship`: you've got to tag two users.
`ShipIt`: another usless ship command works like the one above as well.
`Magic`: messes around with someone's avatar.
`Meme`: gives you a random meme.
`Typerace`: explains itself when used.
`Hack`: you can *totally* hack people with this!!
`Revise`:it shuffles all of the words provided randomly and 
prints it all back out.
`Kill`:you can kill other hoomans with this!
`8ball`:it's just like any other 8ball. *no shit*
`cnjoke`:a random cnjoke.
`dadjoke`:a random dadajoke.
`Snowball`:throws a snowball at a user.
